# Security rules

- Validate all AI outputs with Zod.
- Treat connectors as high-risk: enforce https, allowlisted hosts, and block private network destinations.
- Encrypt secrets at rest (AES-256-GCM) and never return them once stored.
- Rate-limit AI generation, publishing, and connector test endpoints.
- Add audit logs for publish/rollback/connector changes.
- Implement Shopify GDPR webhooks for redaction in production.
